      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00006"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi> (aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs><supplied>)</supplied></addrLine><addrLine>d. Z. <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb462">Venedig</rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40983">Grand Hotel des Bains</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00005"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb45260">Brioni</rs>:</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb52330">Venustempel</rs> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb52316">Val-Catena</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00006"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb45260">Brioni</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>6/8 913</date></dateline></opener><p>Vielen Dank für die ausführlichen Grüße. Ferner: <hi rend="underline" n="1">wie
                  lange</hi> bleiben Sie drüben? Und möchten Sie nicht einmal herüber ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en? zweimal die Woche gehen Schiffe von <rs type="place" ref="#pmb462"><hi rend="latintype">Venedig</hi></rs> hieher, <pb facs="1913_AS_RBH_1_00005"/>einmal <subst><del rend="overwritten">p</del><add place="inline">b</add></subst>ei Tag;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chöne Fahrt.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
